data.description: This stunning home in Cobblestone Park is a dream come true for many. On the main level, the open concept layout offers plenty of room, with a Dining Room, Living Room, Great Room, and Kitchen all connected. The 9-foot ceilings and hardwood floors create a cozy and inviting atmosphere, while the gas fireplace adds a warm touch. Furthermore, this level is complete with a guest room and full bathroom, providing comfort and convenience for visitors. The Gourmet Kitchen is a sight to behold, with its medium brown stained cabinets, complete with crown molding, granite countertops, and a subway tile backsplash. Adding to the spectacular look and feel of the kitchen are stainless steel appliances, a gas range, double ovens, an island, a pantry, and recessed lighting. On the second level of the house, the primary suite features a serene bathroom with a double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, and a large walk-in closet. The three secondary bedrooms upstairs share a hall bathroom, providing plenty of space for everyone. When you step outside, you will be delighted by the secluded fenced backyard with covered porch. Perfect for entertainment, you will enjoy spending time outdoors with friends and family. This resort style community offers amazing amenities to its residents. The 24-hour gated entrance ensures safety and security, while the club house and tennis courts provide plenty of entertainment. Get your daily exercise at the sports complex, playground, or fitness center.
